{"tid":1769592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國電訊宣布叫停所有5G網絡設備採購交易","createTime":"2019-12-05T03:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T15:35:37.000Z","uid":28114,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"468caa8641734ab50e3f5a13d1fe0380f028d442","tid":1769592,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1496039_1_20191205083248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1496039_1_20191205083248.jpg&h=a793b32b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國電訊叫停所有5G的採購交易，等待默克爾政府決定是否禁用華為。（Shutterstock）<br />\n<br />\n歐洲最大電訊公司德國電訊宣布，已經暫停所有5G網絡設備採購交易，等待德國政府討論會否基於安全理由，而禁止向中國電訊設備生產商華為購買零件。<br />\n<br />\n德國電訊回覆路透社查詢時表示，鑒於目前的不明朗政治形勢，公司未有與任何供應商簽訂5G合同。<br />\n<br />\n正在英國出席北約峰會的美國總統特朗普表示，華為是一個安全隱患與威脅。英國首相約翰遜表明保持國家安全至關重要。北約峰會發表的宣言指，將繼續為保障網絡安全和能源安全採取措施，以及保障包括5G在內的通訊系統可靠及安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496039-20191205.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496039-20191205.htm&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=6f6b17f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496039-20191205.htm&h=1326db35\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496039-20191205.htm</a>"},{"pid":"be336d8e835566bc16fa70ac4536b77c788b6c51","tid":1769592,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左膠德國佬終於肯出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a22692fa596508e16d46ad647c8147ae6bec692","tid":1769592,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12